com.github.rholder.moar.concurrent

Interface QueueingStrategy<E>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - the type of elements held in the target queue
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HeapQueueingStrategy

    public interface QueueingStrategy<E>
    Implementations of this class perform actions before and after adding or removing items from a queue (i.e. as a mechanism for slowing or speeding up subsequent adding based on some calculated heuristic).
